data.description: Over 100k in upgrades! Move-in ready stunner in Alta Mesa. Lower level features generous formal & informal living w/ vaulted ceilings, fireplace, spacious updated kitchen w/ granite counters & raised ceiling, sizable bonus room, half bath & charming owner's suite w/ backyard & pool access. Three more bedrooms plus full bath & loft upstairs. Backyard paradise boasts a sparkling pool & housing for equipment, covered & paver patios, low-maintenance landscaping, mature green trees, enchanting lighting & amazing sunset views. Updates galore include a new roof (2018), new AC unit (2023), luxury vinyl plank flooring & carpet (2022), dishwasher & new plumbing throughout (2022), & epoxy garage floor(2021)! Easy access to 202 freeway, highly rated schools, dining, shopping, golf, hiking & more.
